Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:07.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are kept at a distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coarse and mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:13.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They seem to be completely different,\Nfrom the flora and fauna that are familiar to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.49,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This group of strange looking creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.49,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}...has inflicted fear onto humans since long past,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:24.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and have come to be called... "mushi".
