Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:43.11,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone strange is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.71,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,A monkey, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:09.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The green that surrounds me is extraordinarily vibrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.95,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.95,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\be1}The Green Seat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.71,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Once in a blue moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.96,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You will come across a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,who is born with what you might call a predisposition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:39.97,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...to bring forth plants, water— life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(770.8,170.2)\blur1\frz338.6\frx36\fry346}Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like it's safe to write characters,\N even with my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see..."The sunlight has gradually softened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.54,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The trees are beginning to bud, and the birds also..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always been left-handed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's easier to write with this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:17.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn... I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:20.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}These characters are based on drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're so-called pictographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This'll take care of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.19,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Come back here, bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to go outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.33,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.50,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,D-did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, with my very own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you loroi Shinra-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:57.51,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.35,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you read my letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:07.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, then, you're the mushi-shi, Ginko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.93,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was just writing you a reply declining your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:15.97,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Until now, I've had several research solicitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,but I've turned them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the dying wish of my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She said I was not to broadcast my special ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,and, as much as possible, not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:32.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,As you just saw, it's been the case\N that if I draw something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:36.69,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,even if it's a picture of something that doesn't exist, it will come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:43.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But my grandmother said that it's not right for humans to bring a new creature to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,and that it'll anger all the gods and goddesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:50.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So she forbade me from drawing with my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, if I draw with my right hand, nothing happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,but I injured my finger the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's how what you saw earlier happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.20,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.36,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That was one of your amazing creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I never dreamed that even something like that would start moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:10.59,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,although I've had a lot of weird things start to move on me until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.71,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Like an umbrella and a back scratcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to be researched.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:20.38,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.92,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But I won't make you leave this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It must've been hard to trek\N this deep into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stay the night and relax here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And, to be honest, it's been a while\N since I've spoken to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.43,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'd love to hear what's \Nhappening out there in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.87,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's fruit wine that I made myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I usually have some by myself out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.19,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You live all alone in a deserted place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:54.02,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, since my grandmother passed away four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,because she told me I was never to leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.64,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I can see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he were to live in a village...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and accidentally bring to life \Na creature in front of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}they probably won't allow him to lead a peaceful life as he is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.35,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His ability is far beyond human intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.69,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It sounds like your grandmother was a wise person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:25.16,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She always looked out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you take a look at these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You drew these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.17,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:46.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,When I'm by myself, creatures like these sometimes appear out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.97,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always wondered what they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It was fun watching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So I drew some pictures and showed them to Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:04.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand why you always see these phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:08.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's because of that \Nfrightening power you possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget about these phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.95,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,How dreadful... just dreadful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.18,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You poor child...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.36,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all she would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.50,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,and she never believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.08,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,what I saw until the day she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So I myself sometimes wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:32.32,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,if something was wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That was the only thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandma and I couldn't see eye-to-eye about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.73,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...these creatures are all "mushi".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.77,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.91,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.64,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,They're distinct from insects and reptiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me give you an analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.49,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's say these four fingers represent animal life and your thumb is plant life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,At the point farthest from your heart, at the tip of your middle finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:09.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The farther you go down on your palm from there, the lower the life forms become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.52,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,As you continue to go lower, around your wrist, your blood vessels combine into one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.69,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Fungi and microorganisms would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:23.77,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Once you come to that point, it becomes difficult to distinguish between plant and animal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:28.57,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet, there is life still past that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Go up your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...and past your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And, the life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...that is around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...is called "mushi", or "green matter".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,They are similar to life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:51.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Because they are so close to life itself, \Ntheir shapes and existences are ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:55.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Some you can see, some you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. Some are transparent... like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:03.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Even some ghostly apparitions are mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,since some can take on the\N appearance of humans, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:10.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Your grandmother was probably unable to see mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's difficult to share a sensory experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as it's impossible to describe the feel and texture of an object to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.19,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...who has never experienced that feel and texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.13,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not easy to have someone understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.72,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...world of mushi, if they've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But, Grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,you don't know how happy I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:44.09,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2400)}...to have those weird creatures in this world of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now where is the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a rambling house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and pretty old, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm surprised Shinra lives alone in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.04,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just saw something pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:14.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess there's no way this \Nhouse wouldn't have any mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.31,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... you have a mushi pin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going to pin a mushi with that for display?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.32,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You lowly mushi-shi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Lowly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.35,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to be called that by a mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.16,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh-what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.41,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,How can smoke do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.77,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It clings to fellow mushi and won't let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.16,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It disappears right away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a sake cup that's broken...\N but what a pretty color!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you used to drink with this while moon gazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.35,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up. Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.18,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you brazenly come into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure talk big for a mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You're saying... this is your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.53,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:27.57,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Aha! I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:34.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You were once a human, but now you're a creature with mushi characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not a full mushi. \NThat's why you're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And this half piece of green sake cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,it give me a clue as to how you came to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It also tells me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Renzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I did some research on Shinra before I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So I have an idea as to how to \Nmake this sake cup whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Want to hear me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.95,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandma Renzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.54,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandma is still here in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.54,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But not in human form, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:19.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She's in limbo between human and mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:24.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:28.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a phenomenon called the {\i1}Mushi Banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.21,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's where mushi take on human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.52,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And invite guests to their banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.57,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's there humans are given a sake cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,When humans drink the sake they are offered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,they lose the laws of being a living creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,They become inhabitants of the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So Grandma was at one of those banquets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But the banquet was interrupted midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:00.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of that, your grandmother was saved from becoming a mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,but when she returned home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,she was no longer the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:09.27,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She left half of herself on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Shinra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.20,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The grandmother that you knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...was only half of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But the other half was watching over you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:23.82,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...inside this house from the day you were born, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.24,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I... had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Since she isn't fully mushi, you can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:41.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If we use your power, she can\N turn into a complete mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:46.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,though once she does, she will never be able to return to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.27,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it really true if we go through with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I will be able to see Shinra again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.54,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Your grandmother didn't need long to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You will help her out, won't you, Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't watch me draw, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,With your left hand, try drawing the sake cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,that your grandmother received from the mushi at the banquet I described earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What? But you never told me its color or shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Just try drawing using your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.60,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,My imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:37.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be able to draw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The other half of the sake cup your grandmother received
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,should be passed on to her children and grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.82,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When someone tells you not to look, \Nyou just can't help looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I get the feeling it's green...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,just like the green of this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Rich and vibrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:13.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And, it's flat and round in shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:20.84,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's cracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.57,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Renzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.05,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you there, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.08,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to put the halves together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Now drink it, Renzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.24,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you guys so shy all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.81,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She's a lot younger than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:28.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, you take a sip, too. It's a celebratory sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:28.75,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's... Grandma's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to hurry before the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.78,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.73,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't get out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:44.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, drink, loroi Renzu-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.50,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a banquet held in your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.25,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How fragrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With each sip,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lose the ability to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.02,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.42,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That is a living entity called {\i1}Kouki,{\i0} the sake of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:17.09,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It normally dwells deep in the darkness and forms an enormous stream of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:24.09,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,but we created that sake cup, which can extract it, especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:28.82,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It has been gushing out ever since there has been life in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:33.02,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,When it nears soil, it makes \Ngrass green, blows life into buds,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,and when it moves away, the land dries up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.95,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, it's the water of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You will not taste anything more delicious in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:45.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,The reason why we are exchanging a drink and treating you so well
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.27,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,is because we have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:54.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Thirty one years from now, your grandson will be born with a special power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:59.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,which can change the world of living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:04.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,We want you to watch over him for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My grandson...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:12.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That will be best for both him and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:17.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If you agree to this, we will grant you powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:22.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, drink the sake to the last drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.88,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.87,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinra's tears would not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he could feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Renzu's emotions and senses flowing into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:44.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he was just terribly sad \Nthat the sake cup got broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And, as if it's responding to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.95,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kouki, too, continued to flow from the sake cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:58.64,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1700)}{\i1}Ceaselessly, it continued to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa! The ground is covered with moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.45,Alt,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the area that was saturated with {\i1}Kouki{\i0} last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.92,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you giving up your research on Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:25.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I suppose, since a troublesome \Nwatch-guard has been revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You should drop by sometime as long  you don't have any research.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:35.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though it can't be helped, Shinra is probably lonely being in a place like this by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:40.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think that will be necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:44.50,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,because from here on, he'll always have you by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:52.12,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,He left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.93,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Without even saying goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:58.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,We didn't do much to thank him, so I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:04.14,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:08.36,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,...that green sake cup is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thereafter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.78,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I never heard of new rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:19.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}...about the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:21.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with the God-like left hand.
